  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/affliction_21.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Standard-Actions\">standard action</a>, you can touch an&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/classes/core-classes/wizard/arcane-schools/paizo-arcane-schools/classic-arcane-schools/bestia/bestiary/rules-for-monsters/creature-types#TOC-Undead\">undead</a>&nbsp;creature and infuse it with negative energy. It gains a +1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/glossary#TOC-Profane-Bonus\">profane bonus</a>&nbsp;on all attack rolls and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throws</a>, as well as 1&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit point</a>&nbsp;per Hit Die and a +2 bonus to its turn resistance. The bonus on attack rolls and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Saving-Throws\">saving throws</a>&nbsp;increases by +1 for every 5 wizard levels you possess. These bonuses last for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1 round). The bonuses and&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Temporary-Hit-Points\">temporary hit points</a>&nbsp;are immediately dispelled if the creature is within the area of a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/magic/all-spells/c/consecrate\">consecrate</a>&nbsp;spell. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/basics-ability-scores/ability-scores#TOC-Intelligence-Int-\">Intelligence</a>&nbsp;modifier.</p>"
    },
